# Ignore all
*
!*/

# Add metadata and build files
# Package is the repo root itself; rollup_bridge_indexer is a self-symlink (-> .) that
# makes `import rollup_bridge_indexer` resolve. Track it so checkouts/CI/Docker get it.
!rollup_bridge_indexer
!.gitignore
!.dockerignore
!py.typed
!**/Dockerfile
!**/Makefile
!**/pyproject.toml
!**/*.lock
!**/README.md
!**/TESTING.md
!**/CLAUDE.md
!**/.keep

# Add Python code
!**/*.py
**/.*_cache
**/__pycache__

# Add configs and scripts (but not env!)
!**/*.graphql
!**/*.json
!**/*.sql
!**/*.yaml
!**/*.yml
!**/*.j2
!**/*.env.default
!**/*.sh
# Docker smoke-test env fixture: dummy/public values only, used by tests/e2e/smoke_test.sh.
# Allowlisted explicitly so the blanket `.env` exclusion above still hides real secret envs.
!tests/e2e/smoke.env
# Test-stand case env: public endpoints/addresses + block windows, committed so any setup
# can reproduce a case. Allowlisted past the blanket `*` ignore (real secret envs stay hidden).
!tests/stand/tezosx.env
!tests/stand/cases/*/window.env

# Per-developer local Claude Code settings — not shared. Must come AFTER the `!**/*.json`
# allowlist above (last-match-wins) or `.claude/settings.local.json` leaks back in.
/.claude/